readout <- mkwy(readout)

readout %>% dplyr::filter(code=='quag' & run==1) %>% 
  group_by(wy, climmod) %>% summarize_at(vars(precip), list(sum)) %>%
  ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x=wy, y=precip)) + ggtitle("precip")

ggplot(readout[readout$wy<2018,]) + geom_boxplot(aes(x=as.factor(wy), y=lai, fill=climmod)) + facet_wrap('code', scales='free')

ggplot(readout[readout$wy<2018,]) + geom_boxplot(aes(x=as.factor(wy), y=gpsn, fill=climmod)) + facet_wrap('code', scales='free')

readout %>% group_by(wy, code, climmod) %>% 
  summarize(lai=mean(lai)) %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(data=readout[readout$run==1,], aes(x=wy, y=precip/500), fill='grey') + 
  geom_line(aes(
    x=wy, y=lai, col=climmod)) + 
  facet_wrap("code", scales='free')
